--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.1.0, 2010-03-18
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Forked from aewm++ (timestamped 28 December 2008)
    * Abstracted keybindings
    * Toggle windows (Alt-Tab)
    * Close active window (Alt-F4)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.2.0, 2010-03-19
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Improved swapping of workspace
    * Renamed desktop to workspace
    * Removed all menus
    * Windows are tagged a workspace (can belong to several workspaces)
    * A workspace with all windows
    * Shortcuts for accessing workspaces (Mod4+<num>)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.3.0, 2010-03-20
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Updated copyright information
    * Shortcut for toggling tags on focused window (Ctrl-Alt-<num>)
    * Step through workspaces with mouse scrolling
    * Simple bar showing workspaces as boxes with the active one highlighted
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.4.0, 2010-03-22
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Renamed workspacebar to foobar
    * Minor calibrations of foobar geometry
    * Added workspace numbers in foobar
    * Switch workspace by clicking in foobar
    * Runfield to fork programs in foobar (Mod4-r)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.5.0, 2010-03-23
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Removed some of the commandline arguments
    * Rewrote commandline argument parser to use getopt instead
    * Added resource object to handle all X resources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.5.1, 2010-03-23
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Moved source code to separate folder, updated Makefile
    * Updated help output
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.6.0, 2010-04-03
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Added support for special characters in runfield
    * Added aliases to the fork-exec functionality
    * Added debug option to Makefile, cleaned up Makefile
    * Added debug printout when compiled as debug
    * Corrected warnings from valgrind, still memory leaks though
    * Bugfix: foobar could not handle dynamic number of workspaces
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.7.0, 2010-04-05
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Ability to execute actions with aliases
    * Cleaned up all includes
    * Removed ability to iconify clients
    * Improved edge snap and title height macros
    * Bugfix: invalid command line argument during restart action
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.8.0, 2010-04-10
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Preparation for grouping windows
    * Preparation for fork-exec windows with predefined settings
    * Ability to specify workspace to fork-exec in from runfield: "<ws>:<cmd>"
    * Cleaned up old enums and macros
    * Removed ability to set title align in clients
    * Initial implementation of Point class to replace x and y variables
    * Bugfix: decoration line between title and window not drawn properly
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.9.0, xxxx-xx-xx
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Switched all x, y variables to Point objects
    * Cleaned up window initial positioning
    * Made resource pointer global
    * Improved storage of clients/windows in windowmanager for faster access
    * Improved calculation of client title height
    * Bugfix: window instanciated by other window spawns on last used workspace
    * Bugfix: key bindings does not work if caps-lock is activated
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------